stork.feather.util

Class AnonymousResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • stork.feather.Resource<AnonymousSession,AnonymousResource>
      • stork.feather.util.AnonymousResource

  • public class AnonymousResource
extends Resource<AnonymousSession,AnonymousResource>
    A base class for anonymous Resources. AnonymousSessions and AnonymousResources are generally used for creating virtual Sinks and Taps that emit Slices that aren't based on real addressable Resources, yet must declare an associated Resource to work within the framework. This class represents a virtual Resource such implementations may use.
